text: I have no motivation to do anything
I don’t feel like talking to anyone
I have trouble sleeping and feel low
I feel nervous all the time
My heart races and I worry a lot
I panic when things go wrong
I fear something bad will happen
I get irritated by small things
I feel like shouting at everyone
I have no energy to do anything
I am happy with life right now
I am grateful and in a good mood
I don’t know how to feel
I feel lost and not sure what to do
I am unable to decide anything
I am overwhelmed with mixed feelings
